        <p class="text-sm text-amber-300 font-semibold mb-3">C=3, H=4, A=1, K=5, R=1, A=1 · 6 letters · C+H+K power trio</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">An energy centre in the body according to Hindu tradition. CHAKRA delivers 15 points from 6 tiles — 2.5 points per tile. The K=5 provides the core scoring, supported by C=3 and H=4. With two A's and an R as filler, this word is reasonably drawable.</p>
      </div>
